definitions.definition: An expression of one's own physical pain .
examples: Ouch ! You stepped on my toe! That hurt!

definitions.definition: An expression in sympathy at another's pain.
A reply to an insult seen as savage (frequently one that is tongue-in-cheek or joking).
examples: Ouch . How could you say that?
Ouch , I really wanted to do that.

definitions.definition: Expressing surprise at the high price of something.
examples: Ouch , one hundred thousand dollars for a car! I could never afford that!
